  <text>
    <body>
  <div type="scene" n="4">
    <head>SCENE IV.</head>
    <stage type='personnages'>CREON, ATTALE.</stage>
    <sp>
      <speaker>ATTALE.</speaker>
      <l n="1560.2">
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Son couroux seroit-il adoucy&#160;? </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">Son couroux seroit-il adouci&#160;? </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">Son courroux seroit-il adoucy&#160;? </rdg>
      </app>
      </l>

<l n="1561.1">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Croyez-vous, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #D">Croyez-vous </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C">Croyés-vous </rdg>
      </app>
la fléchir&#160;? </l>
    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker>CREON.</speaker>
<l n="1561.2">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Oüy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">Oüi </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">Ouy </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">oüy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">oüi </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">ouy </rdg>
      </app>
mon cher Attale, </l>
<l n="1562">
Il n’est point de fortune à mon bon-heur égale, </l>

<l n="1563">
Et tu vas voir en 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">moy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">moi </rdg>
      </app>
dans ce 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">jour </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">iour </rdg>
      </app>
fortuné, </l>

<l n="1564">
L’ambitieux au 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Trosne </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">Trône </rdg>
      </app>
&amp; l’amant couronné. </l>

<l n="1565">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">Je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Ie </rdg>
      </app>
demandois au Ciel la Princesse &amp; le 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Trosne, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">Trône, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1566">
Il me donne le Sceptre, &amp; m’accorde 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Antigone, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">Antigone. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1567">
Pour couronner ma teste, &amp; ma 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">flamme </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">flame </rdg>
      </app>
en ce 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">jour </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">iour </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1568">
Il arme en ma 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">faveur </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">faueur </rdg>
      </app>
&amp; la haine &amp; 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">l’amour&#160;: </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">l’amour. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1569">
Il allume pour 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">moy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">moi </rdg>
      </app>
deux passions contraires, </l>

<l n="1570">
Il attendrit la Sœur, il endurcit les Freres, </l>

<l n="1571">
Il aigrit leur 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">couroux, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">courroux, </rdg>
      </app>
il fléchit sa rigueur, </l>

<l n="1572">
Et 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">m’ouvre </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">m’ouure </rdg>
      </app>
en 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">mesme </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">même </rdg>
      </app>
temps &amp; leur 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">trosne </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">trône </rdg>
      </app>
&amp; son cœur. </l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker>ATTALE.</speaker>
<l n="1573">
Il est 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">vray, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">vrai, </rdg>
      </app>
vous 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #E">avez </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">auez </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">avés </rdg>
      </app>
toute chose prospere, </l>

<l n="1574">
Et vous seriez heureux si vous 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">n’estiez </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">n’estiés </rdg>
      </app>
point 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Père, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">Pere. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1575">
L’ambition, l’amour n’ont rien à desirer, </l>

<l n="1576">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Mais </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">Mais, </rdg>
      </app>
Seigneur, la nature 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">à </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">a </rdg>
      </app>
beaucoup à 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">pleurer. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">pleurer </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1577.1">
En perdant vos deux Fils… </l>
    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker>CREON.</speaker>
<l n="1577.2">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Oüy, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">Oüi, </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">Ouy, </rdg>
      </app>
leur perte 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">m’afflige, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">m’afflige. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>
<l n="1578">
Je 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">sçay </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">sçai </rdg>
      </app>
ce que de 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">moy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">moi </rdg>
      </app>
le rang de Pere 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">exige, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">exige. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1579">
Je l’estois. Mais sur&#160;tout, j’estois né pour regner, </l>

<l n="1580">
Et je pers beaucoup moins que je ne crois 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">gaigner. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">gagner. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1581">
Le nom de Pere, Attale, est 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">vn </rdg>
      </app>
titre vulgaire, </l>

<l n="1582">
C’est 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">vn </rdg>
      </app>
don, que le Ciel ne nous refuse 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">guere, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">guere. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1583">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">Un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Vn </rdg>
      </app>
bon-heur si commun n’a pour 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">moy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">moi </rdg>
      </app>
rien de 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">doux&#160;: </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">doux&#160;; </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1584">
Ce n’est pas 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">vn </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">bonheur </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">bon-heur </rdg>
      </app>
s’il ne fait des jaloux. </l>

<l n="1585">
Mais le 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Trosne </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">Trône </rdg>
      </app>
est 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">vn </rdg>
      </app>
bien dont le Ciel est 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">avare, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">auare, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1586">
Du 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #C #D #E">reste </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B">Reste </rdg>
      </app>
des Mortels ce haut rang nous separe, </l>

<l n="1587">
Bien peu sont 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #C #D #E">honorez </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B">honnorez </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">d’un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">d’vn </rdg>
      </app>
don si 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">pretieux, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">precieux, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1588">
La Terre a moins de 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Roys </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">Rois </rdg>
      </app>
que le Ciel n’a de Dieux. </l>

<l n="1589">
D’ailleurs tu sçais 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">qu’Hemon </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">qu’Hémon </rdg>
      </app>
adoroit la Princesse, </l>

<l n="1590">
Et qu’elle 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">eust </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">eut </rdg>
      </app>
pour ce Prince 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">une </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">vne </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #D #E">extrême </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C">extréme </rdg>
      </app>
tendresse, </l>

<l n="1591">
S’il 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">vivoit, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">viuoit, </rdg>
      </app>
son amour au mien seroit fatal, </l>

<l n="1592">
En me 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">privant </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">priuant </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">d’un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">d’vn </rdg>
      </app>
Fils le Ciel m’oste 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">vn </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Rival, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">Rival. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1593">
Ne me parle donc plus que de sujets de joye, </l>

<l n="1594">
Souffre qu’à mes transports je m’abandonne en proye, </l>

<l n="1595">
Et sans me 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">rappeller </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">rappelller </rdg>
      </app>
des Ombres des Enfers, </l>

<l n="1596">
Dy moy ce que je 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">gaigne, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">gagne, </rdg>
      </app>
&amp; non ce que je perds. </l>

<l n="1597">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">Parle-moy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">Parle-moi </rdg>
      </app>
de regner, 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">parle-moy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">parle-moi </rdg>
      </app>
d’Antigone, </l>

<l n="1598">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #D #E">J’auray </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">I’auray </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C">J’aurai </rdg>
      </app>
bien-tost son cœur, &amp; 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">j’ay </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">j’ai </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">dé-ja </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">déja </rdg>
      </app>
le 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Trosne&#160;; </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">Trône&#160;; </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1599">
Tout ce qui s’est passé n’est 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">qu’un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">qu’vn </rdg>
      </app>
songe pour 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">moy, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">moi, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1600">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">J’estois </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">I’estois </rdg>
      </app>
Pere &amp; Sujet, 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">ie </rdg>
      </app>
suis Amant &amp; 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">Roy. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">Roi. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1601">
La Princesse &amp; le 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Trosne </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">Trône </rdg>
      </app>
ont pour 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">moy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">moi </rdg>
      </app>
tant de charmes, </l>

<l n="1602.1">
Que…mais Olympe vient. </l>
    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker>ATTALE.</speaker>
<l n="1602.2">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Dieux, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B">Dieu&#160;! </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">Dieux&#160;! </rdg>
      </app>
elle est toute en larmes. </l>
</sp>
</div>
</body></text>
